{"tid":1827454,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"黃色經濟圈要打擊到中資, 就要將重點放係以下兩點","createTime":"2020-01-17T03:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T15:22:40.000Z","uid":64743,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3da60ba4ab88d1f27f041a9d066525298c33421c","tid":1827454,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:18:45.000Z","msg":"其實黃色經濟圈應該重點做<br />\n1. 杯葛連鎖, 商場鋪, 高調支持狗隊等等, 無容置疑既藍店<br />\n2. 擴展至全球, 第一拉攏對象係澳洲, 變成環球本土經濟消費, Everything but China<br />\n<br />\n要收幾多間藍店皮先等如收一間連鎖店皮?<br />\n同埋黃可以扮藍, 藍又可以扮黃, 而事實上, 商人全部都係藍 / 看風使舵, 大家就糾纏係係唔係黃 / 既問題上, 其實係冇乜成效<br />\n明顯黃店當然可以盡力支持, 尤其光時果啲<br />\n但講到對老共有實質打擊, 應該集中杯葛中資大集團業務, 其實有好多覺得避無可避既野可以AMAZON搞掂<br />\n國際層面以我所知華為既市場已經比SAMSUNG吞左唔少, 擴展全球本土經濟消費, 其他貨品都杯葛中國既入侵<br />\n呢個先係我地既戰場"},{"pid":"840a2beb9a935f765f87cd114a71e50dd85bfdb7","tid":1827454,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a69706adc1df9b62c549c1ee5c1b3208ebef63","tid":1827454,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:20:43.000Z","msg":"（重開）如何利用文宣滲入藍色經濟圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de49a9d2f2df118f496c5ef9abf25161a3fea5a8","tid":1827454,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e5abf515faa1e595ff6dc743d334d2bc3293bd","tid":1827454,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59be61d5bf6d5fb9118c8cfedd51daf370d3a8b1","tid":1827454,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc